<h3 id="step-3">Step 3</h3>

<p>After signing up, you will be welcomed to the platform, and you will be required to watch two(2).</p>

<h3 id="step-4">Step 4</h3>

<p>Next you will be asked to a answer 30 question about photostudy policies, and the stipulated number of attempts is maximum of 3.</p>

