<h3 id="step-5">Step 5</h3>

<p>Ater successfully answering the 30 questions, you will be directed to a page where you can choose a subject of your choice. I will advice you start with a question you are most good at, then you get familiar with the platform.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> Number of attempts is maximum of 2 for each subject</p>

<p>The number of questions for each subject may varies.</p>
